max_H = 2*mean_H for n=3,5,6 (all n≥3 except n=4!)
At n=4: max_H = 5/3 * mean_H

Conjectured formula: max_H = n!/2^(n-2) for n≥3, n≠4
  n=3: n!/2^(n-2) = 3.0
  n=4: n!/2^(n-2) = 6.0
  n=5: n!/2^(n-2) = 15.0
  n=6: n!/2^(n-2) = 45.0
  n=7: n!/2^(n-2) = 157.5

