======================================================================
PART 7: max_H SEQUENCE LOOKUP
======================================================================
max_H at n=7 (from 100k sample): 189
189 = 3^3 * 7 = 27 * 7
n!/2^(n-2) at n=7 = 157.5 (not integer!)
189 / (7!/2^6) = 2.400000
189 / mean_H(7) = 2.400000
  where mean_H(7) = 7!/2^6 = 78.75 = 315/4
189 / 78.75 = 2.400000

max/mean at n=7 = 2.400000
  n=3: max/mean = 2 = 2.000000
  n=4: max/mean = 5/3 = 1.666667
  n=5: max/mean = 2 = 2.000000
  n=6: max/mean = 2 = 2.000000
  n=7: max/mean = 12/5 = 2.400000

